title: Jeff Bezos SAVED this Canceled Show! #shorts
description:
What would you do if your favorite TV show was CANCELED?! Cry? Scream? Well, if you’re Amazon founder Jeff Bezos you may just BUY that show and add it to your own streaming platform. This is the lowdown on Amazon’s The Expanse.
